query:
/*+  */ select count(*)
from question AS q
inner join tag_question AS tq
on tq.question_id = q.id AND q.favorite_count >= 0 AND q.favorite_count <= 10000
inner join site AS s
on tq.site_id = s.site_id AND q.site_id = s.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('stackoverflow')
inner join tag AS t
on tq.tag_id = t.id AND t.site_id = s.site_id AND t.name IN ('asp.net-mvc-4',
'audio',
'callback',
'enums',
'ftp',
'garbage-collection',
'linked-list',
'notifications',
'polymorphism',
'react-native',
'react-router',
'split',
'svg');
